AIsolationPollute
/ Writes %shared_probe%=1. Paired with BIsolationProbe. When the outer
/ test.run launches this first (alphabetical + parallel=1), a regression
/ that shared MemoryStack across tests would leak this value into
/ BIsolationProbe's entry state.
- set %shared_probe% = 1
- assert %shared_probe% equals 1
